item.title: CVE-2021-25431|2024-08-03T20:03:05.620Z -- samsung%20mobile -- cameralyzer
item.description: Improper access control vulnerability in Cameralyzer prior to versions 3.2.1041 in 3.2.x, 3.3.1040 in 3.3.x, and 3.4.4210 in 3.4.x allows untrusted applications to access some functions of Cameralyzer.

item.title: CVE-2022-36832|2024-08-03T10:14:28.427Z -- samsung%20mobile -- cameralyzer
item.description: Improper access control vulnerability in WebApp in Cameralyzer prior to versions 3.2.22, 3.3.22, 3.4.22 and 3.5.51 allows attackers to access external storage as Cameralyzer privilege.
